	   <tr><td colspan=2>I can't help you with the leveling.&nbsp;&nbsp;But what one needs to twist ***MORE THAN*** 3 songs.<br><br>1) a fast computer<br>2) a fast connection<br>3) to have your songs hot-keyed (if you don't know how to do that it's one of the message threads further down.<br><br>4) Good timing (hey, and you thought that being a bard would be easy)  You need to time it so that you turn off your song just as/before the effect comes through.  If you get good, you should be able to twist 3 or 4 songs at a time....though I can only do 4 while practicing in down-time, and with zero lag.<br><br>Philoscope<br>Bard of the 17th song . . . no wait 16th . . . .<br>no wait 17th again...this time it should stick. . .<br>Terris-Thule.<br><br>&nbsp;<br>Looking for love.....pity there's so little in humanity.</td></tr>
